Package: tbcascade
Title: TB Preventive Treatment Cascade Descriptive Analysis (Vladimir Oblast)
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("TB Vladimir Study Team", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "noreply@example.com")
Description: Implements the descriptive epidemiological study plan for the
    Vladimir Oblast TB preventive treatment program: ingestion and schema
    validation of the VladKovMur_dataset.csv registry export, derived
    variables (age, adherence, time intervals, cascade-step flags),
    screening-to-outcome cascade analytics with confidence intervals and
    small-cell suppression, and report-ready visualizations.
